{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "格蕾丝 第5话 互相救赎",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "呃啊啊！我要抑制不住……\\n体内的龙了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "呜啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210115_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安德洛墨达",
            "context": "阿德尔潘失控了！\\n怎么办！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "促进融合体活性的结晶……\\n还挺管用的嘛。\\n呵呵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "帕克，你干了什么好事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "你在说什么呢，这不也是\\n你老公研究的一部分嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "是没错。但那是为了\\n促进融合后的龙的活性\\n以拯救生命垂危的实验对象。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "不是用来像那样……\\n强行让龙失控的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "道具取决于怎么使用。不光是这个结晶，\\n还有实验品……甚至包括你老公。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "你说……什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "我就告诉你吧，格蕾丝。\\n你老公真正的临终遗言……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "他说“你这卑鄙小人”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "什么！？\\n难道，杀了他的人是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "没错，就是我。\\n那残次品逃出去的时候，\\n我趁乱亲手干掉了他。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "我一直看他不顺眼。\\n他得到了所有我想要的东西，\\n还笑得那么幸福……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "但是，即使他不在了，\\n你还是不愿意和我一起生活……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "既然如此，至少……\\n要让你死在我手上。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210115_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安德洛墨达",
            "context": "格蕾丝！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "不要……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "事到如今你说什么呢。\\n你不是一直想死吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "没错……但是……我唯独\\n不想死在你手上，绝对不想！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "所以……我要释放\\n他的遗物中蕴含的力量！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210115_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安德洛墨达",
            "context": "那不是那把蕴含\\n大量魔力的剑吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210115_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安德洛墨达",
            "context": "要是释放出那股魔力，\\n这一带会灰飞烟灭的！\\n求你住手啊，格蕾丝！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "别担心。我并不打算\\n拉着你们一起自爆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "这把剑真正的力量是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "嗯！？龙之力……\\n消退了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210115_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安德洛墨达",
            "context": "阿德尔潘恢复正常了……\\n到底是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "这把剑是我丈夫的遗物，\\n也是用来控制“龙锁”\\n这一魔法的工具。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "我们夫妇一直在私下进行研究。\\n为了偿还我们犯下的罪孽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "哈哈……就算这样你也不是好人。\\n你的所作所为不会得到原谅！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "去死吧，格蕾丝！\\n去死、去死、去死、去死！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕克",
            "context": "唔！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "这家伙是“结社”的人……\\n可以的吧，格蕾丝？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "嗯……他理应赎罪。\\n以命相抵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "原来你在这种地方啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "要忏悔的事太多……\\n总是一不小心就待久了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "对不起……\\n让你背负了不必要的罪孽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "如果你是指之前那个男人，\\n那与你无关。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "“结社”是我的敌人。\\n所以我才杀了他。仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "不，和我有关。你的仇恨\\n起源于我……是我的罪孽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "不是你一个人的罪孽。而且……\\n你们夫妇曾试图拯救\\n我们这些实验品吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "我……的确被你拯救了。\\n被那把剑的力量、\\n被你们的研究所拯救了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "没想到……\\n你笑起来还挺可爱的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "你、你说什么呢！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "今后你也要继续复仇之旅吗？\\n拖着这么危险的身体……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "对，直到消灭“结社”为止，\\n我都会一直战斗下去。\\n我除了复仇一无所有。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "即使曾经的幸福不会再来？\\n即使今后只会不断失去？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "没错……我只存在于过去，\\n所以只能这样活下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "我们……说不定真的很像。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "或许吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "我……并不想忘记我丈夫。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "如果要活下去，\\n我想怀着对从我身边夺走\\n我丈夫的一切的恨意而活。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "所以，拜托你了。\\n今后也让我继续恨你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "为了我内心的伤口永不愈合，\\n为了我能一直悲伤下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "你就恨我吧。要不是我从研究所\\n逃出来，你丈夫也不会死。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "那份罪孽，确实该由我来背负。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "你也可以恨我。\\n而我，想偿还那份罪孽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "偿还……是指那把剑吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "是的，我会继续进行研究。即使无法从\\n悲伤中得到救赎，也要从这份罪孽中……\\n我想为此倾尽余生……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "所以，我们就此别过吧……\\n这段时间谢谢你了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "你应该无处可去吧……\\n那就去“圣城”吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "圣城？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "对，那里的王子是个烂好人。\\n他应该能帮助你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "是吗……谢谢你。\\n再会吧，阿德尔潘……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "（我们无法得到救赎……\\n即便是神明，也无法拯救我们。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "（但是，得不到救赎，\\n这正是我们的生存之道……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}